{"tid":618694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我建議香港政府搞個「讓座基金」同「讓座券」","createTime":"2018-04-06T04:18:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T07:58:28.000Z","uid":57376,"like":54,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c208513935de5f6eae9bb1349c871602ba203817","tid":618694,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T04:18:01.000Z","msg":"既然有啲人咁有善心，不如行多一步啦<br />\n政府帶頭成立「讓座基金」同「讓座券」<br />\n每張讓座券都可以兌換成現金，最少廿蚊一張<br />\n咁果啲鍾意叫人讓座嘅熱心人士出錢買券<br />\n然後用張券同人交換座位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢又可以做善事，讓座果個又有得益<br />\n一舉兩得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過問題係果班熱心人事有幾多個肯出錢呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e54159c8a72225c4891548edb5a2f80bbf166ffa","tid":618694,"uid":57376,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T04:19:37.000Z","msg":"有乜理由你迫人讓個座位就得<br />\n我叫你捐錢就唔得先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你肯出錢嘅，我又唔介意賣個位俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e65788c41576a151cd1b85e3616f0a88c9b728b","tid":618694,"uid":55028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e54159c8a72225c4891548edb5a2f80bbf166ffa","tid":618694,"uid":57376,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T04:19:37.000Z","msg":"有乜理由你迫人讓個座位就得<br />\n我叫你捐錢就唔得先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你肯出錢嘅，我又唔介意賣個位俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T04:21:01.000Z","msg":"岩呀我比正價架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24246efb5d092aca0c8c1eded0fd6ab4e6a3d163","tid":618694,"uid":57376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T04:27:04.000Z","msg":"我真係好想睇下果班劫座撚一講到錢就縮果個衰樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c17849f60779b5d657dd1c4e17174aa0ff48a20","tid":618694,"uid":57376,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T04:29:25.000Z","msg":"政府唔搞，不如我地連登仔帶頭搞<br />\n<br />\n以後一遇到劫座撚就叫佢捐錢<br />\n<br />\n最好隨身帶定一張慈善機構捐款表<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9925bd7af1021cfde7fb1fabc7028dbabd1e5c65","tid":618694,"uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T04:36:22.000Z","msg":"劫座撚睇完一定嚇到鳩縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43292241097a4e8114bf182c4d8ff5018f738e5b","tid":618694,"uid":82175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T04:36:40.000Z","msg":"支持 <br />\n就睇下連登除左狙擊 搞慈善得唔得"},{"pid":"5d54294a8acf58fab3fbf09718b2120b3cd0fb9a","tid":618694,"uid":16668,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T04:38:33.000Z","msg":"個個月係tvb 插個節目整返個18區每月讓座之星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,最熱心讓座之星<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39b41b29bdffa63658123bb787373fee00f99415","tid":618694,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d54294a8acf58fab3fbf09718b2120b3cd0fb9a","tid":618694,"uid":16668,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T04: